states.onEnter:
Stream is text/event-stream; charset=utf-8. Events separated by a blank line (

). Each event is a single line `data: <json>`. Parse: split buffer on 

, keep trailing partial in buffer, for each part take the line starting with 'data: ', json.loads the remainder. There is NO `event:` line and NO `[DONE]` sentinel — the terminal signal is the {type:'done'} JSON. Use httpx/requests with stream=True; iterate chunks, decode utf-8, buffer. Headers X-Accel-Buffering:no, Connection:keep-alive, Cache-Control:no-cache are set server-side.
